Thoroughly review the reported Due to NGAs in the Financial Statements;
Verify the implementation of the Programs, Projects, and Activities (PPAs) under this account;
Facilitate the proper liquidation of funds; and
Ensure the prompt return of any unused or unutilized balance to the source agency in adherence to Section 6.7 of COA Circular No. 94-013 dated December 13, 1994.

