Issue demand letter to concerned Accountable Officer to enforce its collection;
Direct the Municipal Accountant to ensure timely recording of all collections and remittances in the correct accounting period; and
Ensure all Accountable Officers (AOs) to exercise due diligence in the collection, remittance and safekeeping of funds otherwise, impose sanctions against erring AOs.

